name    'nonrootlib'
version '0.1.0'
source 'https://github.com/logicminds/puppet-nonrootlib.git'
author 'Corey Osman <corey@logicminds.biz>'
license 'Apache License, Version 2.0'
summary 'A library for puppet users with no root access. This modules sets up a sysinit like directory structure
so that puppet resources like service can be utilized.  This module should be a part of every nonroot module to ensure
a similar directory structure.  See website for more information.'
description 'A set of facts, directories and nonroot hacks to make running puppet under nonroot easier.'
project_page 'https://github.com/logicminds/puppet-nonroot'

